mg.mapviewer.model

Class TrackLogRefApproach

  • java.lang.Object
    • mg.mapviewer.model.TrackLogRef
      • mg.mapviewer.model.TrackLogRefApproach

  • public class TrackLogRefApproach
extends TrackLogRef
    A specific kind of TrackLogRef to reference an approach to a TrackLog. Additionally it references the ApproachPoint, the distance to the approachPoint and the index of the endpoint in the segment.
